# Obstacle Dodge

A fast-paced Unity C# arcade game where you dodge incoming obstacles, survive as long as you can, and try to beat your best score. Playable in the browser or run locally with Unity.

[Play in browser →] https://play.unity.com/en/games/a6322b5e-5f54-4734-95b0-dc4e06979259/obstacle-dodge-novo

## TL;DR
- One-line pitch: Simple, responsive obstacle-dodging with tight controls and progressive difficulty.
- Quick play: Click “Play in browser” to try it instantly.
- Built with: C# · Unity

## Quick Start (Try it now)
1. Try in your browser: click the Play link above.
2. To run locally:
   - Install Unity (recommended LTS, e.g., 2020.3 / 2021.3 — replace with the project Unity version).
   - Clone the repo: git clone https://github.com/viha-coder/Obstacle-Dodge-Game.git
   - Open the project in Unity, open the main Scene (Assets/Scenes/MainScene.unity or the scene you use).
   - Press Play in the Unity Editor.

## Controls
- Move: Arrow keys or A / D
- Pause: Esc
- Lives: 3 hits before restart

## Why play
- Lightweight, polished beginner project with focus on physics, prefab handling, and reliable object lifecycle.
- Includes a published Unity Play build so you can try the game without building.

